<HEADLINE> Albright, Primakov Meet for U.S.- Russia Summit </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, July 27 (Xinhua) -- Russian Foreign Minister Yevgeny
Maksimovich Primakov and U.S. Secretary of State Madeleine
Albright met here Monday night to prepare for the upcoming
U.S.-Russia summit to be held in Moscow in September.
</P>
<P>
"The basic purpose of our meeting tonight will be to prepare
the Moscow summit which begins in five weeks," Albright told
reporters at a joint press conference with Primakov.
</P>
<P>
