Atlantic Treaty Organization) and Russia, and the conflict in
Kosovo between the Yugoslavian government troops and secessionist
ethnic Albanian forces there, she said.
</P>
<P>
Primakov expressed the hope that the forthcoming Moscow summit
will further promote the ties between the two countries.
</P>
<P>
Albright and Primakov are here to attend the one-day 5th ASEAN
(Association of Southeast Asian Nations) Regional Forum (ARF)
which ended here Monday afternoon.
</P>
<P>
They will also participate in a series of post-ministerial
meetings with ASEAN to be held here on Tuesday and Wednesday. Both
Russia and the U.S. are ASEAN dialogue partners. 
