<HEADLINE> Agassi Claims Title in Washington Tourney </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, July 26 (Xinhua) -- Andre Agassi of the United
States captured his third title of the season when he defeated
Scott Draper of Australia in the final of an ATP Tour tournament
here on Sunday.
</P>
<P>
Agassi took just 50 minutes to win his 37th title of his
career, ousting Draper 6-2, 6-0 to win the Legg Mason Classic
title.
</P>
<P>
