<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, July 27 (Xinhua) -- Philippine Foreign Secretary
Domingo Siazon met with U.S. Secretary of State Madeleine Albright
here Sunday evening and discussed issues of importance to both
countries, said a press bulletin released Monday.
</P>
