<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Full Text of White Paper on China's National Defense (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 27 (Xinhua) -- Following is the full text of the
White Paper on China's National Defense issued here today by the
Information Office of the State Council of the People's Republic
of China:
</P>
<P>
Contents
</P>
<P>
Foreword
</P>
<P>
I. The International Security Situation
</P>
<P>
II. National Defense Policy
</P>
<P>
III. National Defense Construction
</P>
<P>
 Defense System
</P>
<P>
 Military Legislative Work
